K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-2: 'gro la chags pas yang dag byed //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-3: lan gcig 'di gsungs dper brjod nas //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-4: de nas lcags kyu mchog dag gis //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-5: yang dag bkug nas padma che //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-6: spyan ras gzigs dbang grol bar 'gyur //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-7: de la 'di ni padma'i lcags kyu chen po'o //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-8: aom mah'a padmo h'um dza hr'i //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-9: de nas bcom ldan 'das 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-10: dbang phyug 'ongs nas slob dpon la mthong ba sbyin
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-11: par byed do // yang na 'od zer gtong bar byed do //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-12: de nas 'di nyid kyi phyag rgyas slob ma rab tu gzhug par bya ste /
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-13: dar dkar pos gos dkar po dang /
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-14: gtsug tor dkar pos mgo bo dkri bar bya'o //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-15: 'di nyid 'jig rten du rab tu brjod nas de nas smros shig ces so //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-16: de nas padma lag pa g-yon du byin nas g-yas
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-17: pas chu snod byin te 'di skad ces brjod par
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-18: bya'o // sangs rgyas thams cad padma che //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-20: 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug /
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-21: de nyid lhan cig brtag par bya zhes so //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-22: de nas phyag rgya chen po bcing ba dang /
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-23: ting nge 'dzin yang bslab par bya'o //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-24: de bzhin gshegs pa'i padma zhes bya ba'i dkyil 'khor chen po'o //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-25: de nas padma'i dkyil 'khor 'byung ste de bzhin du
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20a-26: dkyil 'khor bris nas dbus kyi ze 'bru la nye
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-0: bar 'dug ste stong phrag brgya bzlas @20b par bya'o
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-1: // de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ting nge
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-2: 'dzin ni padma'i 'dab ma rgyas pa de la kun
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-3: tu gzigs par byed pa 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-4: dbang phyug nyid thob par byed do //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-6: de nas dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor 'byung ste de
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-7: bzhin kho nar dkyil 'khor brtag par byas nas dbus
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-8: su padma stong dgod du gzhug go ;de nas padma
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-9: stong po de bcom ldan 'das la dbul bar bya
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-10: ste lan re lan re yongs su bzlas nas so
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-11: // de nas slob ma rab tu bcug nas dam tshig brjod par bya'o //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-12: bu dang slob ma'i ched du yang //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-13: dam tshig nyams par mi bya ste //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-14: dam tshig bdag la brjod par bya //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-15: gang phyir padma'i rnam pa las //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-17: dam tshig gi ni dkyil 'khor ro //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-18: las kyi dkyil 'khor bri bar bya //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-19: mchod pa rnam pa bzhi yis ni //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-20: sangs rgyas thams cad yid kyis mchod //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-21: lus kyis spyan ras gzigs mgon la //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-22: dag gis phyag na rdo rje la //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-23: las las nam mkha'i snying por skyes //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-24: ji ltar sgrub thabs cho gar 'gyur //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-25: bcom ldan 'das 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-26: ri rab lhun po'i ri'i rtse mor 'khod pa rang
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-27: gi ting nge 'dzin gyis kun tu gnas pa'i sku
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:20b-28: thams cad nas de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku brgyad do
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21a-1: de nas dkar po'i phyogs kyi tshes gcig nas brtsams
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21a-2: te rtag tu thams cad dag pa'i ting nge 'dzin
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21a-3: gyis rgyun tu bzlas bas ji srid 'phags pa spyan
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21a-4: ras gzigs dbang phyug mngon du gyur pa de srid
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21a-6: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku rnams 'phros nas sgrub pa
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21a-7: po'i padma'i dbus su 'khod de slar yang de nas
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21a-8: sangs rgyas kyi sku gzhan 'byung ste sgrub pa po
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21a-9: la mngon par dbang bskur ba gnas shing brtan par
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21a-10: 'gyur ro // de nas bdag gi dngos po thams
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21a-11: cad spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug dang mtshungs pa skad
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21a-12: cig de la bde ba dang ldan pa dang /
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21a-13: ji srid du 'phur bar byed do //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21a-14: sems can thams cad dbang du 'gyur zhing tshe dpag tu med par 'gyur ro zhes so //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21a-15: de nas sgrub pa gzhan dang /
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21a-16: las chen po thams cad 'byung ste 'bum bzlas pas
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21a-17: las kyi sgrib pa thams cad rnam par dag par
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21a-18: 'gyur ro // 'bum phrag gnyis bzlas pas mtshams med
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21a-19: pa la sogs pa'i sdig pa thams cad lhag ma
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21a-21: 'bum phrag gsum bzlas pas bsod nams thams cad mngon du 'gyur ro //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21a-22: de nas gnod sbyin gyi dngos grub thams cad dang /
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21a-23: de bzhin gshegs pa la sogs pa'i phun sum tshogs
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21b-0: pa thams cad ni 'bum phrag sum @21b cu rtsa
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21b-1: lnga bzlas pas thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyang
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21b-3: de nas phyag rgya chen po ni mchod rten stong
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21b-4: phrag brgya byas nas mthar cho gas mtshan thog thag
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21b-6: de nas tho rangs de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21b-7: byon nas snying gar rab tu 'jug par byed do
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21b-8: // de nas byang chub sems dpa' so sor rnyed do //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21b-9: de nas zhal du rab tu 'jug par byed do //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21b-10: de nas spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug so sor rnyed do //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21b-11: ma bsgrubs par yang las thams cad du 'gyur ro //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21b-12: thog mar brjod pas gzhan gyi grong dang /
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21b-14: mdzes par spyan drangs pas thams cad bya'o //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21b-15: 'bebs pa la tsandan gyi bdug pas gdon 'bebs so //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21b-16: shi r'ish'a'i me tog gis sems can dbang du byed do //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21b-17: dri bzang po'i me tog gis sems can thams cad rengs par byed do //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21b-18: sa dkar pos bud med do //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21b-19: dri zhim po'i me tog gis chom rkun rengs pa'o //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21b-20: yungs kar dkar po'i sbyin sreg gis ri dvags dang /
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21b-22: yungs kar dkar po gtor bas mig 'phrul ston par byed do //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21b-23: rma bya'i nu mas rmi lam ston par byed do;
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21b-24: ;dus gsum du bzlas pas rmi lam ngan pa 'joms
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:21b-25: par byed do // til gyi sbyin sreg gis sems can thams cad rengs par byed do //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22a-0: bya gag gi gshog pa'i sbyin @22a *//
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22a-1: sreg gis rgyal po dbang du byed do //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22a-2: rgyal po 'khyil ba'i me tog gi sbyin sreg gis 'dod pa thams cad dbang du byed do //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22a-3: bcom ldan 'das 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug

K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22a-6: de nas 'dod pa thams cad thob par 'gyur ro //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22a-7: rgyal po'i btsun mo'i mchog dbang du byed pa la
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22a-8: bud med kyi dbang po'i spu'i sbyin sreg gis so
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22a-9: // bu mo dbang du byed pa la'ang ngo //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22a-10: don gzhan la'ang sbyin sreg dang bcas pas spyan ras
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22a-11: gzigs dbang gi mdun du nyi ma re rer dus
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22a-13: ral pa gyen brdzes kyi rgyud phyi ma las /
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22a-14: chen po thams cad kyi rgyu 'phrul lo ////
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22a-15: de nas sems dpa' chen pos ting nge 'dzin de
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22a-16: nyid sgom bzhin du khro bo'i rgyal po sgrol mas
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22a-17: non pa'i mnyam par 'dzin pa'i gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22a-18: gsungs so // khru lnga pa dang sgo bzhi dang //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22a-19: sgo khyud rta babs nges gnas pa //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22a-20: phyi rol padma'i rnam par bya //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22a-21: de nas kun nas grva rnams su'ang //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22a-22: de ni legs par bsams byas nas //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22a-23: nang gi dkyil 'khor bri bar bya //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22a-24: sngar brjod snying po 'di yis ni //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22a-25: zlos bzhin 'di ni bsrung ba dang //

K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-0: nag po ljang gu'i tshon sna @22b lnga'i; ;phye ma 'jam po rnams kyis ni //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-1: sgrol ma'i rig pas mngon sngags pas //

K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-4: g-yon du ral pa gcig ma bya //

K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-7: yongs su 'dod pas rdo rigs bya //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-8: dri yi phye mas yongs su bya //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-9: rdo rje khu tshur stobs po che; ;gang du 'jig rten gsum cho ga /
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-12: khu tshur rdo rje khu tshur bcas //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-13: de ni g-yas kyi sgo khang du; ;stobs po che ni rab bzhag nas //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-14: nya yis mgrin par stobs po che //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-15: nub phyogs su ni bya ba'o //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-16: g-yas kyi phyi yi sgo khang du //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-17: de bzhin dbang phyug chen po bya //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-18: de la mdung gi phyag rgya dgod //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-19: ji 'dra'i au ma bri bar bya //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-20: lho yi grva gnyis su bya ba //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-21: phyag rgya rnam pa sna tshogs pa'o //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-22: nub dang byang gi grva rnams su //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-23: log 'dren phyag rgya rdo rje 'o; ;byang gi grva gnyis rnams su ni //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-24: mkhas pas rigs kyi phyag rgya bya //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-25: shar gyi grva gcig rnams su ni //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-26: ma mo tshogs kyi phyag rgya dgod //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-27: bhring gi ri ta log 'dren bcas //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-28: de nas ji ltar 'byor pa yi //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-29: cho gas ji bzhin lha rnams mchod //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-30: khro bo stobs chen sgrol mas non //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:22b-31: bzlas pas bdag nyid bsrung bar bya //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-2: blangs nas rang gnas smyung gnas pas //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-3: mkhas pas byang gi sgo khang du //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-4: gtsang ma gang du rab 'jug bya //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-5: blo dang ldan pas spyan drang bya //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-6: khro bo'i rgyal pos thams cad nas //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-7: ji ltar rig pa'i cho ga yis //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-8: tshar bcad rjes su 'dzin pa'i mchog /
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-9: gdon dang lus kyi las rnams ni //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-10: de nyid du ni nges par bya //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-11: tshar bcad dam tshig bde ba 'dri //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-12: gdon 'pho byed dang za byed dang //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-13: gang zhig la la gsod pa dang //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-14: de bzhin sgrib pa sbyang ba dang //

K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-17: mkhas pas las ni stong dag dang //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-18: gdon rnams bod par byed pa dang //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-19: rang gi rigs dang gzhan rigs kyi //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-20: phyag rgya nye bar mtshon par bya //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-22: 'byung po'i tshogs la sogs pa kun //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-23: de nas gtor ma bdug pa sogs //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-24: rgyas pas mngon par mchod byar gyis //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-25: de yis gdon mthong de mchod bya //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-26: phyis kyi dbang las dul ba thob //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-27: skye bos btung ba sbyin sreg la //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-28: sogs pa rnam par gzhom par bya //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-29: shi sha l'an tsa na blangs nas //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-30: gdon thob pa ni 'pho bar bya //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23a-31: srin po rnams kyis byin pa'i mchu //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-0: mthong ba de 'dra'i mtshon rnams @23b dang; ;sha za rnams la ri bong can //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-2: 'jigs pa mthong na sna tshogs pa //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-3: kun tu rnam par lta bar byed //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-4: skem byed gdon gyi rnam 'gyur gang; ;nus dang dpung pa brten pa yi //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-5: dgra bo rnams ni thams cad du //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-6: lha dang mtshon cha'i bya ba ni //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-7: padma byed dang ral pa dang //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-8: dbyug gu bgrang phreng 'jigs pa'i gnas //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-9: ril ba spyi blugs mi thub nyid //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-10: phyag rgya bram ze can zhes bshad //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-11: rtse gsum kun dang zla phyed dang //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-12: ral pa mig la sogs pa dang //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-13: khyu mchog sgra dang drag po dang; ;dbang ldan rnams te bdun du grags //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-14: shakti gdengs ka ba dan dang //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-15: khyim bya de bzhin rma bya'i mjug /
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-16: phyag rgya gzhon nu ma can bshad //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-17: 'khor lo dung dang be con nyid //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-18: ral gri phub nyid nam mkha' lding //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-19: mgo nyid phyag rgya khyab 'jug bshad //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-20: che ba sprin ni lha chen po'i //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-21: bum pa gtun shing de bzhin du //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-22: ngang pa'ang g-yon gzhogs phyag rgya ste //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-23: phyag rgya la hi ri kar bshad //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-24: nam gru rnams dang gtor zan dang //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-25: rgan po gtum po mthong ba ni //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-26: nam gru dkar po rnams kyi rgya //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-27: rang gi gzugs nyid mthong ba ni //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:23b-28: mdangs 'phrog rnams kyi'o lhung bzed dam //
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:24a-0: de nas mchog tu gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'byung ste byed pa @24a *//
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:24a-1: thams cad dge ba la shing gcig gam ni dur khrod gam /

K12D0724-2_H0711-2:24a-3: mthong nas sgrub pa po khros pas sa la ma
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:24a-4: lhung ba'i ba lang gi lci bas dkyil 'khor nye
K12D0724-2_H0711-2:24a-5: bar byugs te re kha gsum der bya'o //

K12D0724-2_H0711-2:49a-0: dkar po'i bco lnga la sa la ma lhung ba'i ba byung gis ba lang gi @49a *//
